00:23:06.639 --> 00:23:08.320
but it wasn't the right answer?

00:23:09.199 --> 00:23:10.800
And so what did you do?

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:13.919
You asked the question again, right?

00:23:13.919 --> 00:23:15.000
And they look at you and they say,

00:23:15.000 --> 00:23:16.440
well, I already gave you an answer.

