on the very steps of the palace of Jezebel

00:24:10.880 --> 00:24:15.160
and God could have protected his servant.

00:24:15.160 --> 00:24:17.160
That's the God that we serve.

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:20.119
He's able to exceeding abundantly

00:24:20.119 --> 00:24:22.040
above all that we ask or think.

00:24:22.959 --> 00:24:25.600
And we find this evening that God says,

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:27.760
what doest thou hear, Elijah?

